text: Saling is an unincorporated community in Audrain County, in the U.S. state of Missouri. ==History== A post office called Saling was established in 1884, and remained in operation until 1904. The community takes its name from Saling Township. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Audrain County, Missouri Category:Unincorporated communities in Missouri
title: Saling, Missouri
